  • 所有已实现的接口:
    android.graphics.drawable.Drawable.Callback, android.view.accessibility.AccessibilityEventSource, android.view.KeyEvent.Callback, android.view.ViewManager, android.view.ViewParent

    public class TextGroupView
extends android.widget.LinearLayout
    By Relin
    Date time 2019-09-05
    Item控件
    使用该控件可以达到快速布局图标+文字+文字+文字+输入+图标
    采用ImageView + TextView +TextView + EditText + ImageView的
    方式来制作类似布局的快速开发，为达到一个控件解决多控件布局的
    速度问题，以此来写这个控件来解决布局者的痛点。
    Item control
    use this control to achieve quick layout icon + text + text + text + image + icon
    rapid development of similar layouts to achieve a single control addressing multiple control layouts of
    speed issues, write this control to address the layout's pain points. < br / >

      • createShape

        public android.graphics.drawable.Drawable createShape(int shape,
                                                      int strokeWidth,
                                                      int strokeColor,
                                                      int solidColor,
                                                      float cornerRadius,
                                                      float topLeftRadius,
                                                      float topRightRadius,
                                                      float bottomLeftRadius,
                                                      float bottomRightRadius)
        创建Shape 这个方法是为了创建一个Shape来替代xml创建Shape. create shape drawable this method create you self background drawable by shape.the same as code in xml.
        参数:
        shape - 类型 GradientDrawable.RECTANGLE GradientDrawable.OVAL
        strokeWidth - 外线宽度 button stroke width
        strokeColor - 外线颜色 button stroke color
        solidColor - 填充颜色 button background color
        cornerRadius - 圆角大小 all corner is the same as is the radius
        topLeftRadius - 左上圆角 top left corner radius
        topRightRadius - 右上圆角 top right corner radius
        bottomLeftRadius - 底左圆角 bottom left corner radius
        bottomRightRadius - 底右圆角 bottom right corner radius
        返回:
